@Comment:	Chi has a hard time getting started on this activity. Mot gives him a lot of different ideas about who to write to but Chi rejects them. Chi ends up going off to his room but comes back for more ideas about what to write. Mot follows Chi to his bedroom to help him write the letter; however , this is not recorded. Chi finally writes what Mot seems to have told him to. There is a lot of comotion going on which is very distracting.
